title: Short Show Zeitle 12/1: Bill Barr, China Space Program, Elliot Page, Arecibo
itunes:title: Short Show Zeitle 12/1: Bill Barr, China Space Program, Elliot Page, Arecibo
description:
On this edition of Short Show Zeitle Jack and Miles discuss Bill Barr admitting there is no evidence of election fraud, China is testing a new engine that can reach anywhere on Earth "within 2 hours", Elliot Page has come out as transgender, and the huge radio telescope in Arecibo has collapsed on itself.
